Parser using Selenium (http://www.seleniumhq.org/) and 
PhantomJS (http://phantomjs.org/) to parse a Webbahnhofstafel 
of the Deutsche Bahn (https://www.bahn.de) and send a push 
notification to a IFTTT app (https://ifttt.com/) if a special
message occurs - especially if a train is late.

Best use with a raspberry PI and cron.